post_text:
Snow, sun, and rain came across the sky;
And we could not believe our eyes.
It is staying on our roads and will make it difficult to drive.
You talked about it this afternoon in your homes, classes, and in even in the halls;
And here it comes with posts, emails, texts, and phone calls.
Maybe delays and closings do not come on a whim;
But rather delays are meant to preserve life and limb.
FCPS will be operating under a two hour delay on 1/30/19.
Any needed adjustments to this schedule will be made by 7:30 am.

